    "description": "<ul><li><p><span class=\"cf0\">You deal <strong>+1</strong> damage on Heavy Hits (or higher) and</span><span class=\"cf1\"> </span><span class=\"cf0\">Critical Hits on Martial Attacks made using Unarmed</span><span class=\"cf1\"> </span><span class=\"cf0\">Strikes or Melee Weapons.</span></p></li><li><p><span class=\"cf0\">When you Miss using a Melee Martial Attack, you gain</span><span class=\"cf1\"> </span><span class=\"cf0\">ADV on the next Melee Martial Attack you make before</span><span class=\"cf1\"> </span><span class=\"cf0\">the end of your turn. You can only gain this benefit once</span><span class=\"cf1\"> </span><span class=\"cf0\">on each of your turns.</span></p></li></ul><p><em><strong>System Tip:</strong> Use on demand macro to apply that effect.</em></p>",
